},{"pid":"ceaab96d5b89baddd88d0cf94d8aa46d15ae3f54","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:32:56.000Z","msg":"26"},{"pid":"b4eaa44eb2e528a0b067631f66c49466f1ec6536","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"27"},{"pid":"728455cba08cc7a8d164afdc19a86880ec7fc055","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"28"},{"pid":"e7f03c97d6323c6b503fd0474090c548b67939a0","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"29"},{"pid":"f252975cdf214bd0686606a753dd3ff6935ed6b5","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"30"},{"pid":"40fa4fa3d16225ef186d97e39e967b89f4196c36","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"31"},{"pid":"042d41f74e752b810b3ffd9ab7ff897f54173413","tid":1272521,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請￼￼￼￼]<br />\n<br />\n已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱<br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=aa8a1ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n新登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=664bda3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=1fbe2da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=69535ad3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=cc004e42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n交表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=94cfd644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試<br />\n<br />\n去入境處交<br />\n各人事登記處同部分智能身份證換領中心都有選舉事務處員工協助市民登記做選民，可以即時填表同遞交<br />\n<br />\n免費傳真方法&nbsp;<br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 /&nbsp;<a href=\"http://FAX.PLUS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFAX.PLUS&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3bb29fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://FAX.PLUS</a>&nbsp;免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=19177763\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂]2019選民登記 推爆佢 7月2號截止<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263306</a><br />\n[/麻煩大家幫手share出去￼￼￼￼]"},{"pid":"c99056b1329ea90ac04ebd97743a08b339210991","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"32"},{"pid":"b5567f09b31a2427c3d39a472544c7830a3d6e87","tid":1272521,"uid":30304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請￼￼￼￼]<br />\n<br />\n已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱<br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=aa8a1ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n新登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=664bda3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=DRclcmm1nwuo18s%2Bf8v8PRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=1fbe2da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.h